+/*****************************************************************************/
+/**
+*
+* This is the memory IO function to mask poll a NPI address for a value.
+*
+* @param	IOInst: IO instance pointer
+* @param	RegOff: Register offset to read from.
+* @param	Mask: Mask to be applied to Data.
